description:
On today's Dan Patrick, DP talks to Mike Florio about NFL expansion teams. Saints Head Coach Sean Payton joins us and sounds off on the officials from Sunday's game. And Former NFL QB Drew Bledsoe tells about the day Brady took over the starting gig in New England.
